📂 predict-next-best-selling-product/
│
├── 📄 README.md                 ← Overview of project (concept, workflow, features, insights)
├── 📄 environment_setup.md      ← Setup instructions (virtual env + DB setup)
├── 📄 requirements.txt          ← Python dependencies
│
├── 🧮 scripts/                  ← Main workflow scripts
│   ├── 01_data_import.py        ← Load raw data (CSV/API → SQLite)
│   ├── 02_data_cleaning.py      ← Clean + preprocess data using pandas
│   ├── 03_sql_queries.sql       ← SQL queries for aggregations, joins, validation
│   ├── 04_feature_engineering.py← Create metrics: growth rate, seasonality, popularity
│   ├── 05_trend_analysis.py     ← Rolling averages, moving sums, product trend detection
│   ├── 06_forecasting.py        ← Predict future sales using regression / ARIMA
│   └── 07_visualization.py      ← Generate heatmaps, trend lines, ranking charts
│
├── 🗄️ database/                 ← SQL database + scripts
│   ├── sales_data.db            ← SQLite database (generated)
│   ├── schema.sql               ← Table creation & schema definition
│   └── sample_queries.sql       ← Common SQL queries for data exploration
│
├── 📊 data/
│   ├── raw/                     ← Original CSVs (Etsy/Shopify/Gumroad)
│   └── processed/               ← Cleaned CSVs or SQL-exported tables
│
├── 📈 outputs/
│   ├── charts/                  ← Generated graphs
│   ├── predictions/             ← Forecast outputs (CSV/JSON)
│   └── reports/                 ← Analysis summaries or dashboards
│
├── 🧠 dashboard/ (optional)     ← Interactive Streamlit dashboard
│   └── app.py
│
└── 🗒️ notes/
    ├── project_plan.md          ← Your planning notes (like the Notion brief)
    ├── data_sources.md          ← Info on datasets (Etsy/Shopify links, schema)
    ├── sql_experiments.md       ← Notes on queries, joins, insights
    └── reflections.md           ← Lessons learned, next ideas
